    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Within another three weeks\nwork of removing the Great North\nern offices now in this city to Mar\nGus, Wash, will be begun. Until\nthe buildings necessary to house\nthe clerks, the auditor, superin-\ntendent and others are completed,\nall those forces will carry on their\nwork in outfit cars.\n\n\nMarcus is about 1913 miles north\nof Spokane, and it is authenticity\nreported that it is the intention Of\nthe Great Northern officials to\nmove practically all it's office\nforces to that place."
    }
